quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,“Alif-Lâm-Mîm
  2,2,"“Ili ndi Buku lopanda chipeneko mkati mwake, ndichiongoko cha (anthu) oopa Allah"
  2,3,"“Omwe amakhulupirira zosaoneka ndi maso (monga Munda wamtendere, Moto, Angelo ndi zina zotere zomwe Allah ndi Mtumiki (s.a.w) adazifotokoza, amapemphera Swala moyenera, ndiponso amapereka m’zimene tawapatsa"
  2,4,"“Ndi amene akukhulupirira zomwe zidavumbulutsidwa kwa iwe, ndi zomwe zidavumbulutsidwa kale iwe usadadze, nakhulupiriranso motsimikiza kuti lilipo tsiku lachimaliziro"
  2,5,"“Iwowo (omwe ali ndi chikhalidwe chotere), ali pachiongoko chochokera kwa Mbuye wawo (Allah), ndipo iwowo ndi omwe ali opambana (pokapeza ulemelero wapamwamba ku Minda ya mtendere)"